Package GAME

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CanvasListener
    CanvasListener is the one responsible for listening mouse/keyboard inputs and for the one who will do the corresponding actions.
    CanvasManager  
    Card
    This "Card" class acts as the object that contains the card's suit, rank and its condition (whether it is faced up or not).
    EnvironmentBuilder
    This "EnvironmentBuilder" class is responsible for painting the current status of the environment of the game.
    LinkedStack
    This "LinkedStack" class acts as the representation of the list of Nodes linked together but with the implementation of stack.
    Location
    This "Location" class is used for locating the coordinates of and region bounded by the card/s in the enviroonment.
    Main
    This "Main" class is the class that holds the static main method of the program.
    MenubarListener
    This class is one responsible for capturing inputs from the keyboard/mouse and doing the corresponding actions needed upon the performance of the action.
    MyFrame
    MyFrame class will hold the main GUI interface of the game.
    Node
    This "Node" class acts as the element or node of the linkedlist made in the "LinkedList" class.
    Solitaire
    This "Solitaire" class holds the deck of cards and the actions needed in the game SOolitaire.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Suit
    This enum Suit restricts the value of the Card objects' classification of suit into four - Diamonds, Hearts, Spades and Clubs.
